    "long_instructions": "### Sound Design Challenge\r\nYou're now a sound designer, and your challenge is to create an immersive soundscape that tells a story using everything you've learned about filters, delays, volume, sequencing, layering, and offsetting sounds.\r\n\r\n🎧 The Scenario:\r\nImagine you’re designing the soundtrack for a scene in a movie. Choose one of these themes:\r\n- Mysterious Forest – A foggy landscape where distant echoes and shifting volumes create an eerie atmosphere.\r\n- Cyber City at Night – A pulsing beat, layered synths, and dynamic filters give this city its futuristic energy.\r\n- Ocean Adventure – Sailing boats, open water, and a mix of rising and falling volumes create the feeling of drifting at sea.\r\n\r\n🎼 Your challenge:\r\n-Sequence your sounds: Arrange different sounds in an order that makes sense for your theme.\r\n- Layer and Offset: Try using rests, delays, and overlapping sounds to make your mix feel more natural.\r\n- Use Effects: Apply filters, delays, and volume changes to add depth to your soundscape.\r\n- Match Sound Lengths: Make sure your layers work together by adjusting lengths so they blend smoothly.\r\n\r\n**Bonus Challenge:** Try making a transition effect—like a build-up before a drop or a gradual shift from calm to intense!",
    "display_name": "Sound Design Challenge",
    "preload_asset_list": null
  },
